 class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℵ₀</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cantor</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">le_of_eq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Cardinal</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ord_le</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">two_power_aleph0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ordinal</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">add_one_eq_succ</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ordinal</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">card_succ</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">card_ord</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">add_one_eq</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">absurd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">cantor</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">aleph0_le_continuum</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
